description:
This is a 25 minute workout called '25 Min Evening Yoga Flow | Daily Routine To Relax & Unwind' from the channel Charlie Follows.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Yoga and Flexibility/Stretching.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Sleep Prep vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Welcome to this 25 min evening yoga flow. This is a gentle yoga practice for mixed levels to help you relax and unwind after a busy day. 

This full body sequence is intended to give your whole body the attention it needs after a busy day to help prepare you for a restful nights sleep.

The sequence includes postures to stretch the whole body, guided at a slow and steady pace to help you relax and unwind. 

I hope you enjoy this evening yoga flow. 

Charlie x
